Yeah.

52
00:06:00,290 --> 00:06:01,800
Who is he ?

53
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,550
He was a neighbor when we were in elementary school.

54
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:09,050
He'd moved away 5 years ago,
 but he came back here, apparently.

55
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,830
Were you a good friend of his ?

56
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:14,560
Yeah, we used to hang out a lot.

57
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:25,200
Hey, Rival.

58
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:30,750
You seem to be on
 top of your game.

59
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:35,900
Well, you should enjoy it while it lasts, 
until our baseball club joins the competition.

60
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:38,100
Our baseball club ?

61
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:40,700
You don't even come to our practice. You shouldn't act tough.

62
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:47,010
Don't worry about that. Once the ballpark is built, I'll come to your practice, too.

63
00:06:47,010 --> 00:06:51,210
After all, I'm busy playing 
both soccer and baseball.

64
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:56,620
Between those, 
I have to go on dates, too.

65
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,990
Why are you acting so vain ?

66
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:03,050
You didn't tell anyone what 
happened the other day, did you ?

67
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,760
What happened the other day ?

68
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:10,200
You know, at the inn where we spent the night, after the outdoor concert.

69
00:07:10,650 --> 00:07:11,400
Hmm ?

70
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:19,200
Oh well. She tells me, "I don't want to go home tonight."

71
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,760
By coincidence, we ended up in the same inn as you two.

72
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,100
You two ?

73
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:25,100
You and Kunimi.

74
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:28,300
And my partner was...

75
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,240
Don't imagine something naughty, okay ?

76
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:35,980
We spent the night purely as 
wholesome high school students.

77
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:38,350
I didn't go to any outdoor concert.

78
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:39,970
Huh ?

79
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:43,650
What ?

80
00:07:46,930 --> 00:07:50,150
Hiro was also with a girl that night.

81
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:53,050
And she was an absolute beauty.

82
00:07:53,050 --> 00:07:55,900
What ? Did you lie to me ?

83
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,120
That's unfair !

84
00:07:57,120 --> 00:08:00,120
You spent the night
 with a girl at that inn ?

85
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,550
Damn you...

86
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:04,000
As for us...

87
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,800
Us...

88
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,000
"As for us" ?

89
00:08:12,930 --> 00:08:15,940
Well, we popular guys have
 our own hardships, I suppose.

90
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,100
Go, go [team name indistinguishable]

91
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:20,600
Oh, it's time for the game.

92
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,830
Now, make sure to cheer for me.

93
00:08:23,730 --> 00:08:29,990
Well, you should enjoy it while it lasts, 
until our baseball club joins the competition.

94
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,370
Our baseball club ?

95
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:35,380
You don't even come to practice. You shouldn't act tough.

96
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:41,190
Don't worry about that. Once the ballpark is built, I'll come to your practice, too.

97
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:43,910
Hey, Kunimi !

98
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:50,200
The girl you spent the night with wasn't Koga, was it ?

99
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,200
Of course not, moron.

100
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,610
It was my big sister.

101
