Look this way, please !

208
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:53,550
What's going on ?

209
00:18:54,530 --> 00:19:00,120
If you could act as his girlfriend for a day, it would be great.

210
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:06,000
He told a friend from his previous school that he had a girlfriend ?



211
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:09,470
And out of the blue, that 
friend is coming to visit him.

212
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,830
Yeah.

213
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:16,630
You're the perfect fit for the
 description he gave his friend, he says.

214
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,550
Do you believe him ?

215
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:24,010
What do you mean ?

216
00:19:24,010 --> 00:19:28,650
He's totally lying to you.

217
00:19:28,650 --> 00:19:30,390
He's my childhood friend.

218
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:32,600
That was five years ago.

219
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:36,470
You should be objective and see what he's like now.

220
00:19:36,470 --> 00:19:42,250
I can bet that this friend
 of his won't show up.

221
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:45,030
I don't want to be
 alone with that guy.

222
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:48,000
No matter how much I ask ?

223
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:51,950
There's something 
wrong with you, too.

224
00:19:51,950 --> 00:19:54,800
Why are you obeying him ?

225
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:56,730
Is he blackmailing you or something ?

226
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,700
I got it.

227
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:04,930
You'll accept it only when
you're going out with Hiro.

228
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:05,610
Hide-chan !

229
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:08,060
That's what it is, isn't it ?

230
00:20:08,670 --> 00:20:08,930


231
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:20,970
